TYPE HORIZON . — Serra da Galga Member, Marília Formation, Bauru Basin (
Fernandes & Coimbra 2000
). Studies based on microfossils (Dias-Brito et al . 2001; Gobbo-Rodrigues et al . 2003) and vertebrates ( Santucci & Bertini 2001 ) agree with a latest Cretaceous (most probably Maastrichtian) age for this stratum.

